      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为金融风控系统画一个呼叫状态机。核心场景是：系统检测到异常后触发外呼，整个通话生命周期要能追踪。起点是FinTech_FraudDetection这个模块，先进入Idle状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_FraudDetection",
        "Idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Idle是等待状态。那外呼动作怎么触发？是从Idle直接跳到Dialing吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Dialing"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Idle到Dialing的触发条件是dial动作。然后Dialing进入Ringing，这个叫calling。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Dialing",
        "Ringing",
        "dial",
        "calling"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Idle--Dialing标注dial，Dialing--Ringing标注calling。Ringing之后呢？用户接听和挂断怎么分支？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Dialing",
        "Ringing"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Ringing有两个出口：用户接听就进Connected，标注answer；如果用户提前挂断，回到Idle，标注hangup。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ringing",
        "Connected",
        "Idle",
        "answer",
        "hangup"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加。Connected之后还有状态吗？比如通话中的保持功能？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Connected"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有的，Connected可以进入OnHold，触发条件是hold；也能直接结束回到Idle，条件是disconnect。OnHold要能resume回到Connected。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Connected",
        "OnHold",
        "Idle",
        "hold",
        "disconnect",
        "resume"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Connected--OnHold是hold，OnHold--Connected是resume，Connected--Idle是disconnect。还有遗漏吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Connected",
        "OnHold",
        "Idle",
